Create a new <httr2_request> by class

Source: R/methods_base_request.R
base_request.Rd

Create a new <httr2_request> by class

Usage

base_request(x, ...)

Arguments

x

A class_endpoint, class_temporal or class_group object

...

Additional arguments

Value

An <httr2_request> object or list of <httr2_request> objects

Examples

care_endpoint("care_enrollees") |> base_request()
#> <httr2_request>
#> GET
#> https://data.cms.gov/data-api/v1/dataset/2457ea29-fc82-48b0-86ec-3b0755de7515/data-viewer?offset=0&size=1
#> Body: empty
#> Policies:
#> • throttle_realm: "data.cms.gov"
#> • error_is_error: <rlang_lambda_function>
